# Service Policy Rules — concise

## Definition
- File: `outputs/docs/03-서비스정책.md`
- Purpose: Single Source of Truth for service policy numbers (수치/제한/보상/주기)
- Owner: PM (all teams contribute); Living Document
- Scope: Service/content policies only (회원, 재화, 참여/제한 규칙)

## Single Source of Truth
- Only this doc contains specific policy numbers and limits.
- Other docs (PRD, Screen Design, User Flows, Design Policy) use conceptual wording and link here.
- Not included in this scope: business targets (KPI/일정) — ok in 원페이저/PRD.

## Contains vs Excludes
- Include: 회원, 재화(에너지/포인트) 획득/사용/소멸, 충전/출석/광고/응모/상점/초대 참여 규칙, 일일·보유 제한 등.
- Exclude: API specs/limits, 에러 코드(→ 개발설계); Screen/UI copy·behavior(→ 화면설계/디자인정책); 약관/개인정보(→ 별도 공개 문서).

## Prerequisite
- `outputs/docs/02-PRD.md` approved.

## Section Gating (inherits 00)
- One policy section per turn; require approval by section title (e.g., "에너지 섹션 진행해").
- Refuse "전체 작성"; no placeholder headings for later sections.
- Keep process text in chat, not in the document.

## Required Sections (suggested)
1) 문서 정보 / 업데이트 시점 / 변경 이력
2) 회원
3) 재화 (에너지, 포인트)
4) 충전
5) 출석 체크
6) 광고
7) 콘텐츠
8) 응모센터
9) 상점
10) 초대

## Writing Rules
- Specificity: use exact numbers and conditions (예: "30초마다 +1", "하루 최대 300회").
- No UI/flow descriptions (팝업 문구, 버튼 상태, 배치 등 금지) — move to 화면설계.
- No implementation details (프리로딩 개수, 타임아웃, 에러 처리 등) — move to 개발설계.
- Update change history table on every modification (날짜/작성자/변경 내용).

